e\">\n        <label for=\"female\">Female</label><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Select Dropdown Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"country\">Country:</label>\n        <select id=\"country\" name=\"country\">\n            <option value=\"USA\">USA</option>\n            <option value=\"Canada\">Canada</option>\n            <option value=\"Mexico\">Mexico</option>\n        </select><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Date Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"birthdate\">Birthdate:</label>\n        <input type=\"date\" id=\"birthdate\" name=\"birthdate\" placeholder=\"Enter your birthdate\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Time Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"appointment_time\">Appointment Time:</label>\n        <input type=\"time\" id=\"appointment_time\" name=\"appointment_time\" placeholder=\"Enter your appointment time\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- File Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"resume\">Resume:</label>\n        <input type=\"file\" id=\"resume\" name=\"resume\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Textarea Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"bio\">Bio:</label>\n        <textarea id=\"bio\" name=\"bio\" placeholder=\"Enter a brief bio\"></textarea><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Credit Card Number Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"credit_card\">Credit Card Number:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card\" name=\"credit_card\" placeholder=\"Enter your credit card number\" pattern=\"[0-9]{16}\" title=\"16-digit credit card number\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Credit Card Expiration Date Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"credit_card_expiration\">Credit Card Expiration Date:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card_expiration\" name=\"credit_card_expiration\" placeholder=\"MM/YY\" pattern=\"[0-9]{2}/[0-9]{2}\" title=\"MM/YY credit card expiration date\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Credit Card CVV Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"credit_card_cvv\">Credit Card CVV:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card_cvv\" name=\"credit_card_cvv\" placeholder=\"CVV\" pattern=\"[0-9]{3}\" title=\"3-digit credit card CVV\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Submit Button -->\n        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    </form>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\nIn this revised form, we've added three secure fields to illustrate the importance of secure form design:\n\n*   Credit card number input field (`<input type=\"text\">`) with a pattern attribute to ensure the input is a 16-digit number.\n*   Credit card expiration date input field (`<input type=\"text\">`) with a pattern attribute to ensure the input is in the format MM/YY.\n*   Credit card CVV input field (`<input type=\"text\">`) with a pattern attribute to ensure the input is a 3-digit number.\n\nThese fields demonstrate how to use HTML5 input types and pattern attributes to enforce secure input formats and prevent users from entering invalid data.\n\nAdditionally, you can use the `autocomplete` attribute to prevent browsers from auto-filling sensitive fields like credit card numbers. For example:\n\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card\" name=\"credit_card\" placeholder=\"Enter your credit card number\" pattern=\"[0-9]{16}\" title=\"16-digit credit card number\" autocomplete=\"off\">\n```\n\nThis will prevent browsers from auto-filling the credit card number field, ensuring that users enter their sensitive information manually.",
