le\">Female</label><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Select Dropdown Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"country\">Country:</label>\n        <select id=\"country\" name=\"country\">\n            <option value=\"USA\">USA</option>\n            <option value=\"Canada\">Canada</option>\n            <option value=\"Mexico\">Mexico</option>\n        </select><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Date Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"birthdate\">Birthdate:</label>\n        <input type=\"date\" id=\"birthdate\" name=\"birthdate\" placeholder=\"Enter your birthdate\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Time Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"appointment_time\">Appointment Time:</label>\n        <input type=\"time\" id=\"appointment_time\" name=\"appointment_time\" placeholder=\"Enter your appointment time\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- File Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"resume\">Resume:</label>\n        <input type=\"file\" id=\"resume\" name=\"resume\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Textarea Input Field -->\n        <label for=\"bio\">Bio:</label>\n        <textarea id=\"bio\" name=\"bio\" placeholder=\"Enter a brief bio\"></textarea><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Social Security Number Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"social_security_number\">Social Security Number:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"social_security_number\" name=\"social_security_number\" placeholder=\"XXX-XX-XXXX\" pattern=\"[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{4}\" title=\"XXX-XX-XXXX social security number\" readonly autocomplete=\"off\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Credit Card Number Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"credit_card\">Credit Card Number:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card\" name=\"credit_card\" placeholder=\"XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX\" pattern=\"[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{4}\" title=\"XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX credit card number\" readonly autocomplete=\"off\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Credit Card Expiration Date Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"credit_card_expiration\">Credit Card Expiration Date:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card_expiration\" name=\"credit_card_expiration\" placeholder=\"MM/YY\" pattern=\"[0-9]{2}/[0-9]{2}\" title=\"MM/YY credit card expiration date\" readonly autocomplete=\"off\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Credit Card CVV Input Field (Secure Example) -->\n        <label for=\"credit_card_cvv\">Credit Card CVV:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"credit_card_cvv\" name=\"credit_card_cvv\" placeholder=\"CVV\" pattern=\"[0-9]{3}\" title=\"3-digit credit card CVV\" readonly autocomplete=\"off\"><br><br>\n\n        <!-- Submit Button -->\n        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" disabled>\n    </form>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\nIn this example, we've incorporated the following best practices for safely handling sensitive data like social security numbers:\n\n*   **Read-only fields**: We've made the social security number, credit card number, credit card expiration date, and credit card CVV fields read-only to prevent users from editing them.\n*   **Autocomplete disabled**: We've disabled autocomplete for these fields to prevent browsers from auto-filling them with sensitive data.\n*   **Pattern attribute**: We've used the pattern attribute to enforce a specific input format for these fields.\n*   **Title attribute**: We've used the title attribute to provide a hint to the user about the expected input format.\n*   **Disabled submit button**: We've disabled the submit button until all required fields are filled to prevent sensitive data from being submitted until it is complete and accurate.\n\nBy incorporating these best practices, we can ensure that sensitive data like social security numbers is handled securely and responsibly.",
